{"tid":1166827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民族黨放棄上訴　陳浩天：司法制度大家都知道，無辦法伸張正義","createTime":"2019-05-22T16:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T03:51:56.000Z","uid":47714,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dfb04b9aabda9f50b19231ae5a890f47325b2cc5","tid":1166827,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T16:29:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/禁民族黨運作-民族黨放棄上訴-陳浩天-司法制度無法伸張正義/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A6%81%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E9%BB%A8%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C-%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E9%BB%A8%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9-%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E4%BC%B8%E5%BC%B5%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%2F&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=1d6a5099\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A6%81%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E9%BB%A8%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C-%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E9%BB%A8%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9-%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E4%BC%B8%E5%BC%B5%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%2F&h=8f465c4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/禁民族黨運作-民族黨放棄上訴-陳浩天-司法制度無法伸張正義/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tin-01_rW4Qb_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftin-01_rW4Qb_1200x0.png&h=a7321e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特區政府在去年 9 月 24 號，引用社團條例，正式禁止香港民族黨運作，民族黨召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝向行政會議上訴，今年 2 回被駁回，他們向法庭申請上訴，以推翻政府決定的期限昨日屆滿。陳浩天回應《立場》時證實，決定不會向法庭提出上訴，「司法制度大家都知道，無辦法伸張正義」。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示若向法庭提出上訴，最終一定會打到終審法院，「無論贏又好輸又好，雙方都一定會上訴到終審法院」，司法覆核「最少要幾百萬」，衡量成本效益後，決定放棄上訴。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天又強調，政府禁止民族黨運作不是法律問題，而是政治事件，他放棄透過司法程序挑戰政府，亦不代表政府的做法正確。"},{"pid":"d5876d6016e2f02ae9ccb4a5779dc6f0f86cb962","tid":1166827,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T18:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede9f3a6158003a4c8b868c1b117c170890f218e","tid":1166827,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T18:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b666ef2b55d3eeac6f126783f44feb1d64959f8","tid":1166827,"uid":173002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T18:53:22.000Z","msg":"強國任意釋法，法庭又袋鼠化，法律已淪為極權嘅刑具。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e8fb1fe0d6af57c112cbf108f05772bd99e88b","tid":1166827,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:22:51.000Z","msg":"沉淪的國土"},{"pid":"083c5766d8e086504791ae01926c24bae807c077","tid":1166827,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17243cdc6e771d3ba39666a9f0ebf35635ac0a36","tid":1166827,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b666ef2b55d3eeac6f126783f44feb1d64959f8","tid":1166827,"uid":173002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T18:53:22.000Z","msg":"強國任意釋法，法庭又袋鼠化，法律已淪為極權嘅刑具。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"德國已經證實香港司法係完全失去法治"}]}